title: New: East of Ely – Came Without
content: With one of the feel good songs of the year already tucked snuggly under their belts, Sydney five piece East of Ely are all set to take 2014 by storm. Closing out the year with new track, Came Without, another slice of Foster The People-esque indie-pop, centred around jagged hooks and stadium ready choruses, there’s no playing down just how important a year 2014 could be for the quintet. Check out Came Without below.
